data.name: label22.Text
data.value: Some barangays may restrict borrowing privileges to registered residents or members of specific community groups. This helps ensure accountability and trust among borrowers and need to present valid ID or Proof that they are residing in the said barangay ex: barangay id, proof of residency

data.name: label16.Text
data.value: Borrowing items may be based on a written agreement or a verbal understanding between the borrower and the owner of the item. The agreement should specify the terms of the borrowing, such as the duration, condition of the item, and responsibilities of both parties.
